data.description: Welcome to 2374 Duncan Avenue.  This Cape Cod style home has the amenities that you have been looking for in your next home. 3 bed rooms, large living room, oversized eat-in kitchen, Spacious fenced in yard, newer furnace/ AC, newer roof, are just several details / updates to this must-see property.  Plenty of space to entertain your guests both inside and out. Enjoy the swimming pool and full wrap around deck. Relax in your own hot tub situated in the integral sunroom.  This home offers a partially finished game room and plenty of additional storage in both the remaining basement areas and walk-up attic. Be in City of Pittsburgh in minutes or the North Hills for shopping and restaurants. Welcome home to 2374 Duncan Avenue. 2 Parcels being sold together.
